{"tid":1197491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月12號 二讀 三讀 惡法生效","createTime":"2019-06-10T03:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T05:18:51.000Z","uid":187578,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5354ffb6473908b3a94cfd1ba54abb63665a93","tid":1197491,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"已fact check。<br />\n［緊急提示］<br />\n🙏🏻真心唔該發岀去，好多人唔知三讀係同一日<br />\n<br />\n恢復二讀辯論和三讀(若法案獲得二讀通過)，通常會在同一次立法會會議進行。<br />\n<br />\n法案如通過首讀、二讀及三讀程序，便獲制定成為法例。除非法案訂明較後的生效日期，否則有關法例經行政長官簽署並在憲報刊登後便可生效。<br />\n<br />\n#即係同一日<br />\n#6月12日<br />\n#神不知鬼不覺咁三讀過埋"},{"pid":"f72bff538d18ac3d014e4e9c11be3037f81b3f87","tid":1197491,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"238092f189aaf000c3e53efbf7ef8790bb00a65d","tid":1197491,"uid":165845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b9264d9ab8cf313141f376c72992ccea5a4a6d9","tid":1197491,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22825270d2f24c14b0853002b75451ed05155304","tid":1197491,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae9f4c15b5d7a89e7be48603c5793d8c0f09f153","tid":1197491,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"其實咁重要的消息，點解D大黨唔出黎講？連社民連都冇講。"},{"pid":"184e0a76caf25c4dcf09ec1962288c3e3ab566f7","tid":1197491,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:15:29.000Z","msg":"一日二讀完就係"},{"pid":"ea0adae29e62747e62b6fb8c7dca263c1d709aab","tid":1197491,"uid":231178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9a054940ed989aa3a93ab2bc5282eaf3ce5c33e","tid":1197491,"uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"